{"tid":2139211,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特蘋果持股升3倍 市值達1000億美元","createTime":"2020-08-04T06:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T07:43:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4548b785ee033cde9d304e3ada299e53db695e5c","tid":2139211,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）全球大流行，讓金融市場動盪不安，不少投資人質疑「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）今年的動作，但其實巴菲特的波克夏（Berkshire Hathaway）長期投資蘋果公司（Apple），在這波股災也沒有動搖，受益蘋果股價近期表現亮眼，巴菲特當年的投資直接翻了3倍，目前其蘋果持股價值超過1000億美元（約2.968兆元新台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n《商業內幕》（Business Insider）報導，波克夏在2016年至2018年間花了約350億美元，買進了蘋果約2.5億股<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n蘋果股價週一（3日）來到435.75美元，漲幅2.52%，公司市值超過1.8兆美元，是全球市值最高的公司。<br />\n<br />\n這同時讓波克夏的蘋果持股價值來到約1068億美元（約3.17兆元新台幣），若以成本350億美元來算，已經翻了至少3倍。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果是波克夏持股最大的部位，市值是第2大的4倍多。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3249373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249373&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=d20a1df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3249373&h=a785049d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3249373</a>"},{"pid":"b47b551d04835c30dd69e74aef7872632d4e487b","tid":2139211,"uid":70888,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"填唔填得返航空股條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4895db37fa47dfa880ccbad72c48c65396e26b","tid":2139211,"uid":77187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47b551d04835c30dd69e74aef7872632d4e487b","tid":2139211,"uid":70888,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"填唔填得返航空股條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo